summary: You know Fearless tour, when @taylorswift is singing Fearless and starts spinning around playing her guitar? Well, when I was...
body:
You know Fearless tour, when @taylorswift is singing Fearless and starts spinning around playing her guitar? Well, when I was younger, I picked up my guitar while performing for a crowd of imaginary people in my room and tried to do the same thing…

I don’t even have to say that I fell, right?

That was the moment I realized I have no coordination.

And that’s it. That’s the story how I hurt my knee while pretending to be Taylor Swift. 🤷‍♀️
